@component('layouts.public', ['title' => 'Refund Policy'])
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Refund Policy</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Last updated: July 2026</p>
    <div style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text);">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">1. Failed Transactions</h2>
        <p>If a transaction fails on our end — for example, due to an issue with our platform or an aggregator's system — the amount will be automatically reversed to your CodeDragon wallet, typically within 24 hours. If a reversal does not reflect within this time, please contact support with your transaction reference.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">2. Incorrect Details Supplied by You</h2>
        <p>CodeDragon is not able to reverse or refund transactions that were completed successfully but sent to an incorrect recipient because of details you supplied in error (for example, a wrong phone number, meter number, or smart card number). Please double-check all details before confirming a purchase.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">3. Wallet Funding</h2>
        <p>Funds deposited into your CodeDragon wallet are non-refundable to your bank account, but remain available in your wallet for use on any service on the platform at any time.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">4. Duplicate Charges</h2>
        <p>If you are charged more than once for the same transaction due to a technical error, contact support with evidence of the duplicate charge (such as a bank statement or payment reference) and we will investigate and reverse the duplicate amount to your wallet once confirmed.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">5. Disputed Transactions</h2>
        <p>If you believe a transaction on your account was unauthorized, contact us immediately so we can investigate. We may request additional verification to confirm your identity before processing any reversal.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">6. How to Request Support</h2>
        <p>To report a failed transaction or request a refund review, please reach us via our <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--text); text-decoration: underline;">Contact page</a>, by email at info@codedragon.ng, or by WhatsApp at +234 806 240 2415, with your transaction reference and account details.</p>
